title: Hyo Yun's One Million Likes
overview: Girls' Generation's Hyo Yun will be starring in her very own reality show, Hyo Yun 1 Million Likes. Hyo Yun 1 Million Likes is described to be a revamped version of Kim Na Young's 10,000 Likes as Hyo Yeon will entertain the audience through her fashion, beauty, and lifestyle tips through Instagram. The mission of which is having a total of million likes.
